<style>

	.area-upper {
		background-color:gray;
		border-width: 10px;
		border-color: gray;
		border-style: solid solid hidden solid;
	}
	

	.area-lower {
		border-style: hidden solid solid solid;
		border-width: 30px;
		border-color: gray;
		background-color:white;
		margin-top: -30px;
		padding: 65px 65px 65px 65px
	}

	.comment-title{
		font-family: 'Monospace';
		font-size: 50px;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.comment-content{
		font-family: 'Times New Roman';
		font-size: 30px;	
		color:gray;
	}

	

	hr {
	  	display: block;
		border: 0;
		border-top: 1px solid black;
		margin: 40px 60px 0px 60px;
		background-color:black;
		color:black;
	}

	br {
		line-height: 150%;
	}

	span.glyphicon-list-size {
    	font-size: 25px;
    	color:gray;
	}

	span.glyphicon-text {
		font-size: 25px;	
		color:gray;
	}
	
</style>

<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-10 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-offset-1" ng-controller="ResumeCtrl">
	
	<div class="area-upper">
		<br><br><br><br>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1">
				<img src="https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/t31.0-8/12132611_10203605166849849_7421108928691160831_o.jpg"
					class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>	

	<div class="area-lower">
		<p class="comment-title">
		<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign"></span> 
			Who Am I?
		</p>
		<p class="comment-content">
			I am a person who makes continuous improvement because I crave for learning new things every single day. New way of thinking would be seen to the fact that I like to bring new ideas to team discussion. I strongly believe that great work needs to be done by a great team with people who always craves to learn new things every single day.
		</p>
	</div>
	<br><br><br><br>




	<!-- Skill -->
	<div class="area-upper">
		<div class="row">
		<br><br><br><br>
			<div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1">
				<img src="http://www.ugc.ac.in/skill/images/pic_6.jpg" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="area-lower">
		<p class="comment-title">
			<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign"></span> 
			What skills do I have?
		</p>
		<p class="comment-content">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 ">
					<ul class="list-group">

						<!-- Skill -->
						<li class="list-group-item list-group-item-success">
							<div class="text-center">
								<span class="glyphicon-text ">Web Skill</span>	
							</div>
						</li>
						<li ng-repeat="skill in skills" class="list-group-item" >
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-glyphicon glyphicon-ok glyphicon-list-size"> {{ skill.category }}</span>
							<span class="pull-right glyphicon-text">{{ skill.name }}</span>
						</li>

						<!-- Language -->
						<li class="list-group-item list-group-item-info">
							<div class="text-center">
								<span class="glyphicon-text ">Language</span>	
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="list-group-item" ng-repeat="language in languages">
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-glyphicon glyphicon-glyphicon glyphicon-globe glyphicon-list-size"> {{language.level}}</span>
							<span class="pull-right glyphicon-text">{{ language.name }}</span>
						</li>					

						<!-- Microsoft -->
						<li class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger">
							<div class="text-center">
								<span class="glyphicon-text ">Microsoft</span>	
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="list-group-item" ng-repeat="microsoft in microsofts">
						
							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book glyphicon-list-size"> {{ microsoft.level }}</span>
							<span class="pull-right glyphicon-text">{{ microsoft.name }}</span>
						</li>					
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</p>
	</div>
	<br><br>


<style>
.carousel-container {
	display: block;
	height: 550px;
	
}
.img-carousel {
    width: auto;
    max-height: 100%;
}
</style>
	<!-- Intern -->
	<div class="area-upper">
		<div class="row">
			<br><br><br><br>
			<div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1 carousel-container">
				 
				  <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
				    


				    <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
				    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox" >
				      <div class="item" ng-repeat="carousel in carousels" ng-class="{active:!$index}">
				        <img ng-src="/assets/{{carousel.url}}" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail img-carousel">
				        <div class="carousel-caption">
        					<h3>{{carousel.name}}</h3>
        					<p>{{carousel.subtitle}}</p>
      					</div>
				      </div>
				    </div>

				    <!-- Left and right controls -->
				    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
				      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
				    </a>
				    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
				      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
				    </a>
				  </div>
				</div>
				
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="area-lower">
		<p class="comment-title">
			<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign"></span> 
			What I have learned in BYTE?
		</p>
		<p class="comment-content">
			Interpreter - Being an intern in BYTE gave me a chance to practice my interpreting skills. Its not only a translating job because there are times where people only translate words by words instead of meaning by meaning.
		</p>
	</div>
	<br><br>


</div>



